&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;We&#39;re looking for a sharp, systems-minded Executive Assistant to support our Chief Investment Officer based in London, and 2 VPs (one in London and one in South Africa). You&#39;ll be embedded in a fast-moving, Slack-first culture where things change quickly, and attention to detail is the difference between smooth and chaotic. You&#39;ll be trusted with sensitive information and high-visibility communications that touch every employee at KoBold.&lt;/p&gt;
